Fails to build with the error `You can't change a configuration which is not in unresolved state!`

The problem is that `ApplyExcludeRules` is being applied directly as part of the Boot plugin being applied. This leads to `VersionManagedDependencies` resolving the `versionManagement` configuration before anyone gets a chance to add dependencies to it. `ApplyExcludeRules` needs to be applied lazily, most likey as a before resolve action.

